@page "/about"
@layout MainLayout

<PageTitle>About Donna - Island Girl in IT</PageTitle>

<div class="about-section">
    <div class="text-center mb-4">
        <span class="header-flower">🌺</span>
        <h1>About Me</h1>
        <span class="header-flower">🌺</span>
    </div>
    
    <div class="story-card">
        <p>Hiii! I'm <strong class="pink-text">Donna Villarin</strong> from the beautiful <strong>Kinatarcan Island</strong> 🏝️</p>
        
        <p>Okay, real talk? IT wasn't my first choice. But here I am, trying my best to learn coding even though I never thought I'd end up here. Some days it's hard, some days I wanna give up, but I'm still going! 💪</p>
        
        <p>Living on an island means limited resources, but that doesn't stop me from dreaming big. I might not be the best programmer yet, but I'm showing up every day and that's what counts. 🌸</p>
        
        <div class="quote-box">
            <p>✨ "She believed she could, so she did... even when it was hard" ✨</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <h2 class="mt-4">💕 Things I'm Learning</h2>
    <ul class="skills-list">
        <li>🐢 C# and .NET (slowly but surely)</li>
        <li>🎨 Making websites pretty with HTML/CSS</li>
        <li>🗄️ Basic databases and SQL</li>
        <li>🤝 Teamwork and communication</li>
        <li>⏰ Time management (trying my best!)</li>
        <li>🌊 Balancing island life and studies</li>
    </ul>
    
    <div class="fun-fact">
        <h3>💭 A Little About My Island Life</h3>
        <p>Living in Kinatarcan means I sometimes struggle with internet connection, but I always find a way to submit my projects on time. Being far from the city has taught me to be resourceful and never give up! 🏝️💖</p>
    </div>
</div>